name: Knocked Up
wikiSummary: A song about the worries of a man who has discovered his girlfriend is pregnant. The main features of the song are; a strong, distinctive drum beat; mood-building gradual crescendos and contrasting distorted guitar solos  The track has quietly become a favourite among fans of the band; it is too long to be released as a single or played on the radio, yet its infiltration and notoriety is tremendous.
wikiText:
A song about the worries of a man who has discovered his girlfriend is pregnant. The main features of the song are; a strong, distinctive drum beat; mood-building gradual crescendos and contrasting distorted guitar solos
 
 The track has quietly become a favourite among fans of the band; it is too long to be released as a single or played on the radio, yet its infiltration and notoriety is tremendous.
